MVP SUCCESS CRITERIA
==================================================

A user should be able to:

1. Create an account.
2. Choose a target language.
3. Learn sentences.
4. Review sentences using SRS.
5. Practice shadowing.
6. Earn coins.
7. Unlock stories.
8. Read stories.
9. Save story sentences.
10. Create goals.
11. Track progress.
12. Create posts.
13. Follow users.
14. Like and comment on posts.
15. Stay motivated through progression and community.

Focus on creating a polished MVP that demonstrates the complete learning loop:

Learn → Earn → Unlock → Read → Review → Share → Progress
